# C4 Architecture - Lead Management System (MongoDB)

This index splits the C4 content into smaller files so each diagram renders independently in GitHub.

## Diagram Index

- Level 1 (Context): `documentacao/c4/01-context.md`
- Level 2 (Container): `documentacao/c4/02-container.md`
- Level 3 (Component): `documentacao/c4/03-component.md`
- Level 4 (Code Flow): `documentacao/c4/04-code-flow.md`
- Data Model (ER): `documentacao/c4/05-data-model.md`

## Modeling Notes

- **Embedding:** negotiation timeline is embedded in `negociacoes.history` for fast read of progression.
- **Referencing:** `leads` references `clientes`, `usuarios`, and `lojas` to avoid duplicated master entities.
- **Business integrity:** a partial unique index enforces only one active negotiation per lead.

